<dtml-var expr="GenerateXMLHeader()">
 <dtml-var expr="GenerateHtmlHeader('Internal Error')">
 <body>

 <h3>You Have Found a Bug in <dtml-var expr="GetProgramName()">!</h3>
 
 <p>This page indicates that <dtml-var expr="GetProgramName()"> has
 encountered an internal error.  This probably is caused by a bug in the
 program.</p>

 <p>Please visit the <a href="javascript: popup_qm_bug_system();">QM
 Tools bug tracking system</a> and check whether someone else has
 already reported this bug.  If no one has, please submit a bug report,
 including the information on this page and as much additional
 information as possible.  If you can, include step-by-step instructions
 for reproducing the problem.  Your assistance with this will help us
 make <dtml-var expr="GetProgramName()"> even better.</p>

 <p>When you are done, <a href="<dtml-var
 expr="GetMainPageUrl()">">click here to start over</a>.</p>

 <dtml-var expr="GenerateStartScript()">
 function popup_qm_bug_system()
 {
   window.open("<dtml-var name="qm_bug_system_url">", "qm_bug_system");
 }
 <dtml-var expr="GenerateEndScript()">

 <hr size="1" noshade>

 <p><b>Exception type:</b>
 <tt><dtml-var expr="web.escape(_.str(exception_type))"></tt></p>

 <p><b>Exception value:</b> 
 <tt><dtml-var expr="web.escape(_.str(exception_value))"></tt></p>

 <p><b>Stack trace:</b></p>
 <pre><dtml-var expr="web.escape(traceback_listing)"></pre>

 <dtml-var expr="GenerateEndBody()">
</html>

